Class StopWatch

  • java.lang.Object
    • q3.StopWatch

  • public class StopWatch
extends java.lang.Object

    Stop Watch

    Creates a GUI Stop Watch from the StopWatchPanel. Tests the stop watch. The Stop watch has 3 buttons to control it, start, stop, and clear.

    Version:
    1.0 Dec 7, 2016
    Author:
